    ],
    "The following year his Ph.D.": [],
    "was granted from Columbia, his dissertation on the topic terminology of ancient Greek art.": [
        [
            0,
            3,
            [
                "Was"
            ]
        ]
    ],
    "He wrote the volumes on ancient art for the ground-breaking \"Sources and Documents\" series in 1965 and 1966.": [],
    "In 1969 he was made associate professor at Yale.": [
