    "He chaired the department of Classics for the 1971-1972 year (and a second time 1974-1975).": [],
    "His 1972 introduction to classical art, <em>Art and Experience in Classical Greece</em>, brought his reputation as a progressive scholar to a wide range of students.": [],
    "In 1973 he was promoted full professor.": [
